Uses of Package
mork

Packages that use mork
mork   
 

Classes in mork used by mork
Dict
          A dictionary contains key/value pairs.
Event
          For each element the MorkParser has recognized, an Event is fired.
EventListener
          The Event Listener Interfaces is notified of Parser Events when the Mork Parser parses Mork elements like Dictionaries, Tables, Rows etc.
EventType
          The MorkParser fires events and each event has a type EventType and an optional String value.
Group
          Represents a single group, which has an identifier and its content as String.
Row
          A Row can be located either in the root of Mork files or in tables.
ScopeTypes
          Mork specifies scopes.
Table
          Parses a Mork table, which has a table identifier and contains multiple rows.
